org.pikater.web.experiment

Interface IExperimentGraph<I,B extends IBoxInfoCommon<I>>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - See IBoxInfoCommon.
    B - The box type this graph type supports. "Client" and "server" versions are available.
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<B>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExperimentGraphClient, ExperimentGraphServer

    public interface IExperimentGraph<I,B extends IBoxInfoCommon<I>>
extends java.lang.Iterable<B>
    Interface common for both client and server experiment graph formats. The graphs have oriented edges.
